he methylation status of NR3C1 promoter, gene expression, blood plasma cortisol levels, and adulthood MDD. The study was conducted with 29 MDD patients (9 males, 20 females) and 33 normal individuals (7 males, 26 females). Bisulfite pyrosequencing on 7 CpG dinucleotides in the region showed significantly higher methylation levels at the CpG7 in MDD patients. When separated by gender, the methylation levels differed significantly in females, but not in males. No significant differences between NR3C1 gene expression level and plasma cortisol levels of MDD patients and normal controls were observed. These data suggest that higher levels of methylation at the NR3C1 promoter may be associated with MDD in a gender-specific manner.", "pubmed-id": "26782558", "prism:coverDate": "2015-12-29", "prism:aggregationType": "Journal", "prism:url": "https://api.elsevier.com/content/abstract/scopus_id/84952673665", "dc:creator": {"author": [{"preferred-name": {"ce:given-name": "M.", "ce:initials": "M.", "ce:surname": "Nantharat", "ce:indexed-name": "Nantharat M."}, "@seq": "1", "ce:initials": "M.", "@_fa": "true", "affiliation": [{"@id": "60028190", "@href": "https://api.elsevier.com/content/affiliation/affiliation_id/60028190"}, {"@id": "100830070", "@href": "https://api.elsevier.com/content/affiliation/affiliation_id/100830070"}, {"@id": "60028190", "@href": "https://api.elsevier.com/content/affiliation/affiliation_id/60028190"}], "ce:surname": "Nantharat", "@auid": "57031952400", "author-url": "https://api.elsevier.com/content/author/author_id/57031952400", "ce:indexed-name": "Nantharat M."}]}, "link": [{"@_fa": "true", "@rel": "self", "@href": "https://api.elsevier.com/content/abstract/scopus_id/84952673665"}, {"@_fa": "true", "@rel": "scopus", "@href": "https://www.scopus.com/inward/record.uri?partnerID=HzOxMe3b&scp=84952673665&origin=inward"}, {"@_fa": "true", "@rel": "scopus-citedby", "@href": "https://www.scopus.com/inward/citedby.uri?partnerID=HzOxMe3b&scp=84952673665&origin